spanGrp.span: They were in their way forty five days, hungry and thirsty.
One part of them has died and another part got to villages.
bir uji öldi bir uji ištem čätın gäldi čıhtılar kövlärä
When they got to the villages, there were no houses, nor job, nor anything.
kövlärä gäldılär nä yapılari var nä iš var nädä biše
Only hunger and thirst existed there.
One part of them went to Russia.
sorada ištem genä čätın čätın yašamahlar
